snippet.title: Warcraft III: Reforged Now Live (EU)
snippet.description: Warcraft® III: Reforged™ is a complete reimagining of a real-time strategy classic. Experience the epic origin stories of Warcraft, now more stunning and evocative than ever before. Play now at https://playwarcraft3.com/
